1/21/opinions/hillary-clinton-citizens-united-more-democracy/index.html","headline":"Hillary Clinton: Supreme Court rulings threaten democracy","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/160121001846-citizens-united-protest-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/19/opinions/generation-opinion-roundup/index.html","headline":"Which generation has it worse?","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/150512210808-71-seventies-timeline-0512-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"\u003cem>Editor's Note: Generation whining has become nearly a national pastime. \u003cem>\u003c/em>\u003ca href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/national/archive/2014/03/here-is-when-each-generation-begins-and-ends-according-to-facts/359589/\" target=\"_blank\">Millennials\u003c/em>\u003c/a>\u003cem> say they have it the worst. \u003c/em>\u003cem>\u003ca href=\"http://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2014/06/05/generation-x-americas-neglected-middle-child/\" target=\"_blank\">Generation X\u003c/em>\u003c/a>\u003cem> feels neglected. \u003c/em>\u003ca href=\"http://www.phillymag.com/news/2013/12/13/baby-boomers-worst-generation/\" target=\"_blank\">\u003cem>Baby boomers\u003c/em>\u003c/a>\u003cem> are tired of being called narcissistic. In \u003c/em>\u003cem>\u003ca href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2011/05/bill-clinton-there-are-no-great-generations-just-different-problems/239293/\" target=\"_blank\">articles\u003cem>\u003c/a>\u003c/em> and cartoons everywhere -- from \u003ca href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/09/opinion/bors-millenial-comic-strip/\">\u003cem>\u003c/em>CNN\u003cem>\u003c/a>\u003c/em> to \u003c/em>\u003cem>\u003ca href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/23/fashion/an-online-generation-redefines-mourning.html?hpw&rref=fashion\" target=\"_blank\">The New York Times\u003c/em>\u003c/a>\u003cem> to \u003cem>\u003c/em>\u003ca href=\"http://gizmodo.com/5851062/generation-x-is-sick-of-your-bullshit\" target=\"_blank\">Gizmodo\u003c/em>\u003c/a>\u003cem> and beyond -- critics call out this generation's sense of entitlement, that generation's \u003c/em>\u003cem>\u003ca href=\"http://nymag.com/news/features/my-generation-2011-10/\" target=\"_blank\">self-absorption\u003cem>\u003c/em>\u003c/a>. We invited writers, activists and CNN contributors from \u003ca href=\"http://www.esds1.pt/site/images/stories/isacosta/secondary_pages/10%C2%BA_block1/Generations%20Chart.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">\u003c/em>\u003cem>different generations\u003c/em>\u003c/a>\u003cem> to hash it out.  \u003c/em>","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/20/opinions/pakistan-attack-kugelman/index.html","headline":"Why extremism still haunts Pakistan","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/160120073302-07-pakistan-attack-0120-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/21/opinions/alexander-litvinenko-case-gerstein/index.html","headline":"Troubling truth beneath Litvinenko headlines","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/160121090903-litvinenko-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/21/opinions/bociurkiw-aid-workers-mental-health/index.html","headline":"Aid workers suffer mental health crisis ","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/160112155848-aid-workers-syria-madaya-aid-lkl-paton-walsh-00020015-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"Recently when aid workers finally reached the \u003ca href=\"http://www.cnn.com/videos/world/2016/01/12/aid-workers-syria-madaya-aid-lkl-paton-walsh.cnn\">besieged city of Madaya in Syria\u003c/a>, they saw the horror of destruction and the desperation among the estimated 42,000 inhabitants. The sight of emaciated civilians, deprived of proper nutrition for months, brought tears to their eyes. ","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/18/opinions/moriarty-levinson-family/index.html","headline":"Why did Iran prisoner swap not include my father?","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/130513085823-robert-levinson-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"This past weekend, the United States concluded negotiations for a prisoner swap that resulted in the release of four Iranian-Americans being held by Iran, and a fifth man, a student held 40 days. My father,\u003ca href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2014/03/05/world/robert-levinson-fast-facts/\"> Robert Levinson\u003c/a>, who went missing in Iran nearly nine years ago, was not one of them.","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/05/aviation/emirates-flight-catering/index.html","headline":"Inside the world's biggest airline food factory","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/160106102009-emirates-food-card-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/16/tennis/roger-federer-australian-open-tennis/index.html","headline":"Roger Federer: 'I need to be pushed'","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/160116190037-roger-federer-giant-racquet-melbourne-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"He arrived in Melbourne with a cold and a new coach, but Roger Federer believes he is prepared to contend for the Australian Open title.","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/07/health/male-birth-control-pill/index.html","headline":"How the 'male pill' could actually work","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/150506205107-birth-control-pill-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"\"The Pill\" -- two words synonymous with birth control. But more than 50 years after oral contraceptives became commonplace, they remain an option only available to women. ","layout":""},{"uri":"/2015/12/21/architecture/most-anticipated-buildings-of-2016/index.html","headline":"9 buildings set to define cities in 2016","thumbnail":"http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/151215103039-world-trade-center-transportation-hub-calatrava-small-11.jpg","duration":"","description":"","layout":""},{"uri":"/2016/01/11/foodanddrink/hong-kong-mcdonalds-nex